Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.66,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Prismatic Forest Grotto—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:52.21,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Within it is a legend, \Nspoken of only in whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.17,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The mysterious monster-bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:57.80,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,the Rabbit-Eared Shoebill!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:01.72,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Does this legendary bird really exist?!
