Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.52,Default,Animalia,0,0,0,,The mysterious monster-bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:21.32,Default,Animalia,0,0,0,,We'll use all of SF-Zoo's animal \Nknowledge to find it, or die trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:23.70,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Captain! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:30.91,Default,Animalia,0,0,0,,Is this... a footprint from \Nthe Rabbit-Eared Shoebill?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.29,Default,Animalia,0,0,0,,Looks more humanoid than bird-like...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:38.50,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Following the footsteps, \Nthe expedition moved further into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.05,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,And that's when they heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.10,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Captain! That call...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:50.39,Default,Animalia,0,0,0,,It must be the Rabbit-Eared Shoebill!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The piercing call caused \Nthem to tremble in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.02,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,And then they saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:02.90,Default,Animalia,0,0,0,,We found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:03.78,Default,Animalia,0,0,0,,Let's chase it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:04.57,Default,All,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:11.33,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,They were unable to get \Na clear image on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:15.33,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,But the Rabbit-Eared \NShoebill truly did exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:18.42,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Their desperate search proved in vain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.84,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,and they were unable to \Nget a clear shot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:27.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, the Animalia \NExpedition's search continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Some day, they would find \Nthat mysterious animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:42.03,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Man, watching that huge beetle send \Nyou flying was hilarious, Sunraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:44.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm just glad I survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:48.32,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,I'm still not sure that I did!
